Package gamer

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CurrentSphere
    This class represents the current sphere, and contains its x and y coordinates.First it shows the Sphere1 coordinates, after the robot gets that, it shows Sphere2 coordinates.Then Sphere3, and after all the spheres, it shows the Goal coordinates.
    Goal
    This class represents the goal/objective/end, and contains its x and y coordinates.
    Proto
    The robot's class.This class contains methods to make Proto move, jump, climb, scan the scenario, etc.
    Sphere1
    This class represents the sphere 1, and contains its x and y coordinates.
    Sphere2
    This class represents the sphere 2, and contains its x and y coordinates.
    Sphere3
    This class represents the sphere 3, and contains its x and y coordinates.
